data.description: Lovingly maintained home in Schertz loaded with the important updates! New vinyl siding, fascia & soffits in 2023 (impact resistant & maintenance free)! ALL windows replaced 2019. A/C replaced 2021. Roof and gutters replaced 2017. Gutter filters added 2020. Radiant barrier installed in attic in 2019. Enjoy the large back yard with mature trees. Covered deck added 2019. Deck extended & fence replaced in 2022. Giant master bedroom has two walk-in closets. All bedrooms are upstairs & have C-fans. Kitchen has very large island and lots of counter space. Huge walk-in pantry-utility room.  This home is convenient to I-35 (easy commute to New Braunfels or San Antonio), 1604, shopping, restaurants, and JBSA Randolph. Home comes with Olshan Lifetime transferable foundation warranty.
